title: Pink Panther Classic Cartoons - Disc 1of5 - Part 1of7 (4:3 NTSC)
description:
Pink Panther Classic Cartoons - Disc 1of5 - Part 1of7 (4:3 NTSC)

I will be uploading all 5 discs in the coming weeks..... Stay Tuned!!




-The Pink Phink 1964-

"The Pink Panther disagrees with a decorator (The Little Man) over what color a house should be: blue or pink."


-Pink Pajamas 1964-

"The Pink Panther sneaks into a house to stay the night and has to hide from its drunk owner."

-We Give Pink Stamps 1965-

"The Pink Panther hides in a department store and spends the night trying to hide from the janitor."

-Dial "P" For Pink (Part 1of2) 1965-

"A burglar tries to steal a safe where the Pink Panther is hiding."
